'''肖恩·埃尔德里奇'''（{{lang-en|'''Sean Eldridge'''}}，{{bd|1986年|7月31日|||catIdx=Eldridge, Sean}}<ref>[http://www.facebook.com/seaneldridge Official Facebook page]</ref>）是一位[[美国人|美国]]投资者和政治活动家。他是哈德遜河投资基金会（{{lang|en|Hudson River Ventures}}）[[总裁|总裁]]及“[[结婚自由|结婚自由]]”组织高级顾问。<ref name="Freedom to Marry Staff Bios">{{cite web |url=http://www.freedomtomarry.org/pages/staff#seldridge |title=Freedom to Marry Staff Bios |work=[[Freedom_to_Marry|Freedom to Marry]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20120509230407/http://www.freedomtomarry.org/pages/staff#seldridge |archivedate=2012-05-09 }}</ref>他也是一个推动金融改革的集团“维护我们的民主”（{{lang|en|Protect Our Democracy}}）的创始人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/25/nyregion/with-cuomo-new-group-will-push-for-publicly-financed-elections-in-new-york.html  |title= With Cuomo, a New Group Will Push for Publicly Financed Elections |date= June 25, 2011 |work= [[New_York_Times|New York Times]]}}</ref>

==早年生活与教育==
埃尔德里奇成长于[[美国|美国]][[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[托莱多_(俄亥俄州)|托莱多市]]，[[高中|高中]][[毕业|毕业]]于渥太华希尔斯高级中学（{{lang|en|Ottawa Hills High School}}）。高中毕业后他先后就读于[[深泉学院|深泉学院]]和[[布朗大学|布朗大学]]，2007年成为[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年大选]]参选者[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]竞选团队中的一员，在大学里组织成立了全国性学生组织支持奥巴马的竞选。大学毕业获得学士学位后进入[[哥伦比亚法学院|哥伦比亚法学院]]继续深造，但在[[纽约州参议院|纽约州参议院]]于[[2009年12月|2009年12月]]投票否决了[[纽约州同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]立法后退学，加入了一个名叫“结婚自由”（{{lang|en|Freedom to Marry}}）的支持同性婚姻活动组织。<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.toledoblade.com/Culture/2011/02/27/Former-Ottawa-Hills-resident-to-wed-Facebook-co-founder.html  |title= Former Ottawa Hills resident to wed Facebook co-founder |date= February 27, 2011 |work= [[Toledo_Blade|Toledo Blade]]|accessdate=April 27, 2011}}</ref>

==职业生涯==
埃尔德里奇是哈德孙河投资基金会的总裁，该基金会是一个专注于[[哈德孙河|哈德孙河]]谷的小型商业投资基金会。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.LoHud.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=2011112100309 |title= Scenic Hudson has new board members |date= December 9, 2011 |work= [[The_Journal_News|The Journal News]]}}</ref>他也是“[[结婚自由|结婚自由]]”组织的高级顾问，该组织旨在实现美国全国的婚姻平等，尤其支持[[美国同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]合法化。他于2010年加入该组织，起初担任公关部主任，后来在2011年争取[[纽约州同性婚姻|纽约州同性婚姻]]立法期间担任政治部主任。<ref name="Freedom to Marry Staff Bios"/>他曾经在[[福克斯新闻频道|福克斯新闻频道]]和[[夜线|美国广播公司新闻夜线]]的节目上与[[LGBT法律|同性恋者合法权利]]的反对者展开论战。<ref>{{cite web |author=Video (8:47 minutes; requires [[Adobe_Flash_Player|Adobe Flash Player]])|url=http://video.foxnews.com/v/4416810/judges-ouster-stirs-debate/ |title= Judges Ouster Stirs Debate —  Iowans Vote Out State Judges over Same Sex Marriage Ruling |date= November 12, 2010 |work= [[福克斯新闻频道|Fox News]]|accessdate=January 19, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Video (5:33 minutes; requires [[Adobe_Flash_Player|Adobe Flash Player]])|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Nightline/video/same-sex-marriage-legalized-panelists-debate-gay-rights-11369921?tab=9482930&section=1206872&playlist=7578045&page=2 |title= Should Same Sex Marriage Be Legalized? — Part 1: Panelists Debate over the Right For Gays To Marry |date= August 10, 2010 |publisher= ''[[夜线|ABC News Nightline]]''|accessdate=January 19, 2011}}</ref> 《[[纽约观察家|纽约观察家]]》[[周报|周报]]把他列入[[纽约市|纽约市]]“最有影响力的男同性恋者”前50位名单。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.observer.com/2011/06/new-yorks-new-power-gays-the-top-50/#slide12 |title= The New Power Gays: NYC’s Top 50 |date= June 21, 2011 |work= [[New_York_Observer|New York Observer]]}}</ref>[[2012年6月|2012年6月]]，他创办了“维护我们的民主”组织，旨在关注纽约州的金融改革。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/25/nyregion/with-cuomo-new-group-will-push-for-publicly-financed-elections-in-new-york.html  |title= With Cuomo, a New Group Will Push for Publicly Financed Elections |date= June 25, 2011 |work= [[纽约时报|New York Times]]}}</ref>

埃尔德里奇和他的男友、[[Facebook|Facebook]]共同创始人之一、后来成为他的丈夫的[[克里斯·休斯|克里斯·休斯]]在全美为进步组织和候选人投资。<ref>{{cite web |author=[[Staff_writer|Staff writer]]|url= http://www.advocate.com/News/Daily_News/2010/11/29/Freedom_to_Marry_Doubles_Up/  |title= Gay Rights Orgs Double Up |date= November 29, 2010 |work= [[The_Advocate|The Advocate]]|accessdate=January 19, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/2011/05/01/2011-05-01_andy_intertwines_fundraising_push_for_gay_marriage.html?r=news/politics/ |title= Cuomo focuses on gay marriage but nothing deters a the chase for millions of dollars |date= May 1, 2011 |work= [[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/02/nyregion/cuomo-fund-fills-with-money-from-thankful-gay-donors.html?pagewanted=all |title= After Pushing Gay Marriage, Cuomo Is Thanked With Money |date= December 1, 2011 |work= [[New_York_Times|New York Times]]}}</ref>2009年，他俩共同出席了奥巴马总统为欢迎[[印度|印度]][[印度总理|总理]][[曼莫汉·辛格|曼莫汉·辛格]]到访而举办的总统任内首场[[国宴|国宴]]。<ref name="advocate">{{cite web |author=[[Staff_writer|Staff writer]]|url= http://www.advocate.com/article.aspx?id=102977 |title= A Place at the State Dinner Table |date= November 24, 2009 |work= [[The_Advocate|The Advocate]]|accessdate=January 19, 2011}}</ref>他俩的净资产估计超过7亿[[美元|美元]]。<ref name=Forty>{{cite web |url= http://www.advocate.com/Print_Issue/Cover_Stories/Chris_Hughes_and_Sean_Eldridge/ |title= Forty Under 40: Chris Hughes and Sean Eldridge |date= May 2011 |work= [[The_Advocate|The Advocate]] |accessdate= April 15, 2011 |archive-date= 2011-04-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110414110730/http://advocate.com/Print_Issue/Cover_Stories/Chris_Hughes_and_Sean_Eldridge/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>他们创立了特洛斯基金会（{{lang|en|Telos Foundation}}）。<ref name="Freedom to Marry Staff Bios"/>在[[2011年3月|2011年3月]]，他俩的事迹成为《[[倡导者|倡导者]]》（{{lang|en|''The Advocate''}}）[[杂志|杂志]]的封面故事之一。 <ref name=Forty/>

埃尔德里奇还担任关注哈德孙河谷的最大环保组织“秀美哈德孙”（{{lang|en|Scenic Hudson}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://scenichudson.org/news/release/international-business-and-social-media-leaders-add-heft-scenic-hudson-board-2011-12-7 |title=International Business and Social Media Leaders Add to Heft of Scenic Hudson Board |date=December 7, 2011 |access-date=2012-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426040445/http://scenichudson.org/news/release/international-business-and-social-media-leaders-add-heft-scenic-hudson-board-2011-12-7 |archive-date=2012-04-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>以及“[[支持与保护同性恋者|支持与保护同性恋者]]”（{{lang|en|Gay & Lesbian Advocates & Defenders}}）组织的顾问。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.baywindows.com/index.php?ch=community&sc=gay_and_lesbian_advocates_and_defenders&sc2=news&sc3=&id=121901 |title= Eldridge and Clark join GLAD Board of Directors |date= July 6, 2011 |work= Bay Windows }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>2012年他创立了“领导纽约州负责政府”（{{lang|en|New York Leadership for Accountable Government}}）组织，这是一个由商业和公民领袖组成的旨在推动纽约州金融改革的集团。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/02/15/wealthy-donors-join-effort-to-improve-campaign-finance-system/ |title= Wealthy Donors Join Effort to Improve Campaign Finance System |date= February 15, 2012 |work= New York Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://polhudson.lohudblogs.com/2012/02/15/group-forms-to-push-for-campaign-finance-reform/ |title= Group Forms to Aid Campaign Finance Reform Push |date= February 15, 2012 |work= Politics on the Hudson}}</ref>

据说在2011年埃尔德里奇曾打算与[[南·海沃思|南·海沃思]]（{{lang|en|Nan Hayworth}}）在纽约州众议员第19选区中展开竞赛。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.politickerny.com/2011/07/27/democrat-emerges-to-take-on-nan-hayworth/ |title= Democrat Emerges to Take On Nan Hayworth |date= July 27, 2011 |work= PolitickerNY }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>他将代表纽约州众议员第19选区参加2012年民主党全国代表大会。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.politickerny.com/2012/01/11/which-new-yorkers-are-obama-delegates/ |title= Which New Yorkers are Obama Delegates? |date= January 11, 2012 |work= PolitickerNY |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120112022614/http://www.politickerny.com/2012/01/11/which-new-yorkers-are-obama-delegates/ |archivedate= 2012年1月12日 }}</ref>

==私人生活==
埃尔德里奇与休斯于[[2011年1月|2011年1月]]在[[纽约市|纽约市]]举行的支持“结婚自由”组织招待会上宣布[[订婚|订婚]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nypost.com/p/pagesix/engaging_news_of_facebook_WiG3nVdPBWd8oNNIuLDmuJ |title= Engaging News of Facebook |date= January 15, 2011 |work= [[纽约邮报|NY Post]]}}</ref>他俩于2012年6月30日正式[[结婚|结婚]]。 <ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.advocate.com/Print_Issue/Cover_Stories/Chris_Hughes_and_Sean_Eldridge/ |title= Forty Under 40 |date= May 2011 |work= [[The_Advocate|The Advocate]] |accessdate= 2012-07-16 |archive-date= 2011-04-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110414110730/http://advocate.com/Print_Issue/Cover_Stories/Chris_Hughes_and_Sean_Eldridge/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

